tags: just a thought which came into my mind
body:
Ok, mindblowing thought:

What if Captain Marvel is somewhere in space and Loki met her at some point? And he is currently the only one who knows where she is? He fakes his death so Thanos won’t go after him or something like that, he travels to her, informing her that the universe needs her help and they both travel back to earth to reunite with the Avengers to make a plan to defeat Thanos. And she doesn’t question Lokis request to come with him, cause she got the message from Fury and is totally ready to kick some purple grape’s ass.

body:
Welcome to Episode 22 of the MCU ComsicCast! The long dry spell for MCU news has finally come to an end, as Marvel has kicked off their Captain Marvel promotion with the first magazine cover featuring official images from the film.

This week on the podcast:
